## Unreleased

- Auto-copy `src/index.html` → `public/index.html` on `zig build` (create `public/` if missing)
- Add `zig build clean` step (removes zig-out, .zig-cache, and public)

## 0.1.1 (2026-04-17)

- Browser back/forward navigation via History API (URL reflects current path)
- Right-click on filename to copy link (native browser context menu)
- Text file inline viewer for 30+ extensions (txt, md, json, py, zig, sh, yaml, ...)
- Add .claude/ to .gitignore

## 0.1.0 (2026-04-17)

Initial release.

- Zig 0.15.2 HTTP server with zero runtime dependencies
- Vue 3 Composition API frontend embedded in binary via @embedFile
- Directory listing with sort (name, size, modified) and live filter
- File download support
- Path traversal protection via realpathAlloc + prefix check
- Configurable --root, --port, --host flags
